  "text": "Saturation solubility studies of pure drug and all batches of nanoparticles were studied in distilled water. The result of pure drug and all batches of nanoparticles were shown in Table 3 . Results indicated that solubility of all batches of the nanoparticles increased as compared to pure drug [CITATION_1] . SEM photograph was shown in fig. 3 . SEM has shown that the nanoparticles were small, spherical and porous in nature. The SEM image of fenofibrate powder appeared as smooth-surfaced, irregularly shaped, flat crystals in shape. However, the converted solid nanoparticles appeared as smoothsurfaced particles indicating complete adsorption of lipids containing amorphous drug inside the pores of Eudragit L-100 polymer.",
